                  <div id="innerbodycontent" class="row nolayout"><div class="offset1 span10">
            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>The "shi... de" construction for emphasizing details</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=%22Shi..._de%22_construction&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="&quot;Shi... de&quot; construction">&quot;Shi... de&quot; construction</a>)</span></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASGE662E" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGE662E"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="B1_grammar_points" title="B1 grammar points"> B1</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK1_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK1 grammar points">HSK1</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="B1_grammar_points" title="B1 grammar points"> B1</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK1_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK1 grammar points"> HSK1</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="The_&quot;shi..._de&quot;_construction_for_indicating_purpose" title="The &quot;shi... de&quot; construction for indicating purpose">The "shi... de" construction for indicating purpose</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="./The_&quot;shi..._de&quot;_patterns:_an_overview" title="The &quot;shi... de&quot; patterns: an overview">The "shi... de" patterns: an overview</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Using_&quot;de&quot;_(modal_particle)" title="Using &quot;de&quot; (modal particle)">Using "de" (modal particle)</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="The_&quot;shi..._de&quot;_construction_for_indicating_purpose" title="The &quot;shi... de&quot; construction for indicating purpose">The "shi... de" construction for indicating purpose</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="./The_&quot;shi..._de&quot;_patterns:_an_overview" title="The &quot;shi... de&quot; patterns: an overview">The "shi... de" patterns: an overview</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Using_&quot;de&quot;_(modal_particle)" title="Using &quot;de&quot; (modal particle)">Using "de" (modal particle)</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK4</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Referring_to_the_past" title="Referring to the past">Referring to the past</a>, <a href="Emphasizing" title="Emphasizing">Emphasizing</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="是" title="是">是</a>, <a href="的" title="的">的</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/27/Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/27/Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/27/Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-shi.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<dl><dd><em>Also known as: 是⋯⋯的结构 (shì...  de jiégòu), 是⋯⋯的 sentence&#160;and 是⋯⋯的 pattern.</em></dd></dl>
<p>The 是⋯⋯的 (shì... de) construction is used to draw attention to certain information in a sentence. It's often used to ask questions that seek specific information, or to explain a situation by emphasizing a particular detail. While not strictly tied to any "tense," the 是⋯⋯的 construction is frequently used when asking or telling <i>details</i> about the past.
</p><p>This use of 是⋯⋯的 (shì... de) is usually emphasized in textbooks over other uses, and therefore is sometimes called the "classic" 是⋯⋯的 construction.
</p>
